Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:20.78,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Garnet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:22.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,Amethyst: ♪ Amethyst
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:23.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl: ♪ And Pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:36.63,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,天气不错啊,是吧?\NLovely day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:39.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,还行吧\NYeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:42.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你造,我爸爸告诉过我\NYa know,uh, my dad told me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,到了一定岁数这种事就会发生的\NI should probably expect this at some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但我也没想到会是一夜之间那么快\Nbut I didn't think it would happen overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对啊,不错\NRight, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.01,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮!我秃了!\NConnie, I'm bald!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:57.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦 发生了什么事?\NOh. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:00.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,没事 只是个笑话而已\NNothing.It was just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:02.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,好吧\NOh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:04.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿,你还好吗?\NHey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:07.13,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文,康妮!\NSteven, Connie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.16,0:01:11.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,希望你们准备好学习今天的特殊课程了\NI hope you two are ready for today's special lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.63,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,不,我是不是应该带什么东西来着?\NOh, no, was I supposed to bring something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:14.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,带上自己就好\NJust yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:16.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,石榴会参与旁听\NGarnet is going to sit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:20.04,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,能看你俩作为史蒂翁妮战斗她非常激动\NShe's very excited to see you fight as Stevonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:21.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦!对啊!\NOh! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:23.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,融合训练\NFusion training.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:25.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我做了个口号板\NI made a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:27.25,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这面是为你们俩加油\NThis side is for both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:29.25,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这面是为史蒂翁妮加油\NAnd this sideis for Stevonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:30.85,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,一体两面的\NIt's two signs in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:32.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,融合口号\NA fusion sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:34.59,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,融合笑话!\NFusion joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:37.32,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗?\NReady, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好了,老师\NYes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:42.10,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-康妮!-好了,老师!\N-Connie!-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:45.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文!康妮!喔!\NSte-ven! Con-nie!Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:47.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,启动融合舞蹈\NInitiating fusion dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:49.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:51.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,来打我啊,孩子们\NCome at me, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:58.31,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.32,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不如跳舞\NLet's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,准备...开始!\NLet us...begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:19.70,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哈?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.64,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦!\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:24.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好棒!\NAll right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂翁妮有悬浮能力了!\NStevonnie's got floating powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:29.04,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是时候干掉你了!\NTime to finish the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:33.61,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哈?我很抱歉!\NHuh?I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文!康妮!\NSteven! Connie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.25,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,发-发生啥事?\NW-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:42.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗯啊!\NMmmuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:45.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮,等下!\NConnie, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.70,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿,你怎么了?\NHey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:58.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我在学校做了很糟糕的事\NI did something terrible at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,现在不知道该怎么办\Nand I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:02.01,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘛,听起来不像你的风格\NWell, that doesn't sound like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.24,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,发生了什么?\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.21,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我打了一个同学\NI beat someone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:07.21,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啥?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,一个不认识的小孩\NA kid I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他在走廊上撞到了我\NHe just bumped into me in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我吓了一跳,然后战斗本能被激发了\NI was so startled,my training instincts kicked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我反击了\NI just reacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我觉得太丢人了,就跑掉了\NI was so embarrassed,I just ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是你不是有意伤害他的!\NBut you didn't mean to hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我知道那种感觉\NI know what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,有时候,你会不小心伤害到别人\NSometimes,you hurt people by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:29.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你-你不去想它就好了\NY-you just have to try not to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,先别说话\NHold the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.64,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,交给我来说\NNow give the phone to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:39.31,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,融合能正常存在,取决于平衡\NFor a fusion to work,there needs to be balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:41.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不平衡会导致你的融合\NAn imbalancecan cause your fusion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.68,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,失去对现实的把握\Nto lose touch with reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:46.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,产生各种幻觉,最终破碎解体\Nsee things that aren't there,and eventually fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:49.32,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,也就是说,你俩其中一个迷失的话,\NThat is to say,if one of you is falling apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们的融合也会解体\Nyour fusion will as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:54.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,为了找到平衡,你们必须了解自己的情感\NTo find balance, you must understand your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,为了了解自己的情感,你们需要透彻地看待它们\NTo understand your feelings,you must see them clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.67,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,而不是逃避它们\Nwithout running from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,透彻地看?\NSee them clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我会展示的,不过首先,我们需要史蒂翁妮来\NI'll show you,but first, we'll need Stevonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.31,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-嗯-嗯\N-Mm.-Mm.
