Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文,我准备好训练了!\NSteven,I'm ready to train!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我很高兴和石榴谈话了\NI'm so glad we talked to Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.68,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我想到该怎么做了!\NI really figured outwhat I needed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我和杰夫谈过了!\NI talked to Jeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他叫杰夫,顺便说一下\NThat's his name,by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇,你做到了\NWhoa, you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:11.09,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我道歉了,他也理解我了\NI apologizedand he understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.72,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他事实上还想让我给他表演几招\NHe actually wanted to know if I could show him some moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-很不错啊\N-That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.89,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,想来真有趣\NIt's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:19.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我花了那么多时间沉浸在不安中\NI spent all that time feeling bad
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,却没有采取任何行动\Ninstead of doing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好像我越是试着不去想它\NIt's like I was trying not to think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,事情就变得越糟\Nand that just made it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.70,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,现在我思绪清晰了,\NNow that I've got a clear head,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们作为史蒂翁妮会表现出色的\Nwe'll do so much better as Stevonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不说了,我得换衣服了!\NAnyway,I'm gonna change!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.08,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,很棒的技巧,史蒂翁妮\NGreat technique, Stevonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,继续保持!\NKeep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,谢谢夸奖,老师!\NThanks, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗨呀!\NHyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.76,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃,啊...\NUh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,哦,啊...\NOh, oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:56.63,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,不\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,又开始了!\NIt's happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她是谁啊?\NWho was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:03.24,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是铋斯姆--史蒂文--哦,不\NBismuth -- Steven -- oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这次是我的问题了!\NIt's coming from me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-史蒂翁妮!-啊\N-Stevonnie!-U-uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.17,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,深呼吸!\NBreathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,发生了什么?\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他们怎么了?\NWhat's happening to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:11.91,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他们能做到的!\NThey've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:15.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对,我-我能-呃\NY-yeah,I'm...I'm...ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,铁石英\NJasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我-我试着帮你来的\NI-I tried to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.72,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是你选择不听的\NYou wouldn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.13,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我-我说过让你停下!\NI--I told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.13,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我-我也别无选择!\NI-I had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:30.10,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我-我很抱歉!我不该--\NI-I'm sorry.I shouldn't be --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不!没关系的!\NNo! It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:34.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,想这些事没关系的!\NIt's okay to think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:37.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我以为没关系的,但是我承受不住!\NI thought I could,but it's so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我做不到!\NI can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啊!\NAhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.34,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啊!\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:52.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:56.59,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂翁妮!\NStevonnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:02.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们在坠落!\NWe're falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.13,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文,和我融合!\NSteven, let's fuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们能悬浮的 我们会没事的!\NWe can hover.We'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文?\NSteven?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我没有想伤害任何人!\NI didn't want to hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉!\NI'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.87,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她们没有一个接受我的帮助!\NNone of them would let me help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:14.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我也别无选择!\NI had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.31,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,没关系的!\NIt's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不!有关系!\NNo, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但你回想这些事是可以的!\NBut it's okay to think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.78,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,感觉太难受了\NIt feels so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那也没关系!That's okay, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:25.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当时你也没有其他的选择!\NThere was nothing else you could have done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.55,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我不想感觉这么糟\NI don't want to feel this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你不得不\NYou have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你需要正面对待这些糟糕的情感\NYou have to be honest about how bad it feels
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:32.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这样才能跨过去\Nso you can move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我就是这么做的\NThat's how it was for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,深呼吸就好\NJust breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗯-\NMm-mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.67,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我在这里\NI'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪♪
